# Intuition
In this program our main intution is to calculate the median of the array as we know that it is efficient case to make all array element equal to the median value so that cost can be minimum.As all the values will be at fair distance from the median element both largest and the smallest Value.


# Approach
so we first calculate the median and then find the cost of each element that each element will take to get transform to median element.
The totalcost will be our answer.
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
- O(NLOGN)
