# Intuition
Changing all the elements to the median element is optimal. We can consider cost as the element's frequency to calculate the median.

for eg - nums = [2,1,3,4] cost = [4,2,1,3]
To calculate median, we can consider the array as -
[2,2,2,2,1,1,3,4,4,4]
Sorting the array to calculate the median ->
[1,1,2,2,2,2,3,4,4,4] , hence the median is **2**

# Complexity
- Time complexity : $$O(NlogN)$$
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

- Space complexity : $$O(N)$$
